data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the fabulous Canyon Creek gated community! This stunning residential single-family home is a masterpiece of modern living, offering a perfect blend of luxury, convenience, low maintenance, and energy efficiency. Amenities on site consist of: community pool, clubhouse, exercise room, and the security provided by gate. Newly built in 2019, meaning up to date and ready for you and the family to just pack your bags and move on in. Schedule your private showing today!
